      title: 'Shopify Smart Search Guide | Best Search Apps 2026',
      description: 'The ultimate guide to Shopify Smart Search. Learn how to optimize site search, choose the best Shopify search app, and increase conversion rates in 2026.',
      keywords: ['Shopify smart search', 'smart search Shopify', 'Shopify search app', 'Shopify product search', 'Shopify search optimization', 'Shopify site search', 'best Shopify search app'],
